Cross-Border Stablecoin Register (CBSR) — dual license
=======================================

This project is dual-licensed so that the dataset stays citable (attribution
required) while the tooling stays permissively reusable.

DATA  — all `*.yaml` records, the corridor file(s), the compiled `dataset.json`,
        and the generated coverage tables (`COVERAGE.md`, `records.md`):
        Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International (CC-BY-4.0).
        See LICENSE-DATA.  SPDX-License-Identifier: CC-BY-4.0

CODE  — `build.py`, `record.schema.json`, and any other tooling/scripts:
        Apache License 2.0.
        See LICENSE-CODE.  SPDX-License-Identifier: Apache-2.0

When in doubt about whether a file is "data" or "code": records and the dataset
are data; anything that processes them is code. The two full license texts live
in LICENSE-DATA and LICENSE-CODE respectively, and are also referenced from the
README and CITATION.cff.

Copyright 2026 Yunjie Fan.
